description:
The blessing of the Sound Fist Seeklave. Base attack power increases
by 200%. The effect is canceled when Seeklave is destroyed.
name: Blessing of Seekref

description:
The protection of the Sound Armor Affabile. Base defense power
increases by 300%. The effect is canceled when Affabile is destroyed.
name: Guardian of Affabille

description:
The protection of the Sound Armor Affabile. Base defense power
increases by 200%. Despite being defiled time and again, there are now
signs of wear in its once impregnable defense.
name: Echo of Affabille

description:
Can be used when grappled by an enemy or downed. In an emergency,
unleash a burst of magical power to escape from a pinch.
name: Burst

description:
Charge attack. A narrow frontal range magical damage attack with a
punch imbued with magical power.
name: Forte

description:
An obscene earring attached to Ganuron's favorite pregnant women. A
humiliating ornament unfit for a noble lady.
name: Slave's Earring

description:
A distinctive tattoo applied to an orc's favorite toy. Known to all
adventurers, those who see it cannot avoid contempt and ridicule.
name: Orc Slave Crest

description:
About the body's reactions and weaknesses due to sexually transmitted
diseases and training. An objective description of responses to
specific acts and physical changes.
name: Body

description:
Delicious homemade cooking using fresh ingredients nurtured by the
rich nature of the hot spring town. It naturally brings forth
strength.
name: Buff: Innkeeper's Special Dish

description:
A baked confectionery similar to cookies, made by kneading wheat with
milk and baking it. The drizzled syrup adds a simple sweetness.
name: Buff: Simple Baked Sweets

description: The belly is only slightly swollen, hardly affecting movement at all.
name: Debuff: Early Pregnancy

description:
The swelling is clear enough to be seen over clothes. Its weight
hinders Serena's movements, and she instinctively protects her belly.
name: Debuff: Mid Pregnancy

description:
The belly is swollen to an extent unimaginable from her fairy-like
delicate beauty, hindering daily life activities. Combat is out of the
question.
name: Debuff: Late Pregnancy

description:
Catherine was drenched in the 'universal medicine' she had created.
The overwhelming pleasure that painted over the pain was,
nevertheless, still pain.
name: Aphrodisiac Addiction

description:
Fear or intense disgust towards specific actions, creatures, or
places. Reinforcement of emotions such as loathing, fear, and
screaming.
name: Heart

description:
You find yourself obeying Gekuran's words. It's still a mild state,
and you can resist if you feel discomfort.
name: Gekuran's Hypnosis - Mild

description:
You obey Gekuran's words and offer yourself to him. Feelings of
discomfort and disgust fade, and you begin to accept Gekuran's
existence.
name: Gekuran's Hypnosis - Moderate

description:
If it's Gekuran's words, you'll accept anything. Repeated hypnosis and
training are beginning to invade even your tastes and common sense.
name: Gekuran's Hypnosis - Training

description:
Your mind is almost completely subdued by Gekuran. One more push and
Serena's heart will be completely conquered, even forsaking her vows.
name: Gekuran's Hypnosis - Severe

description:
Your rebellious spirit against the city guards is completely
shattered. Hearing their voice makes your heart shrink, and your body
stiffens and trembles with fear. You probably can't even fight back.
name: Trauma - City Guard

description:
Your heart and body have been completely dominated by Ganuron's
physique and dick. Resistance is futile, begging for mercy is futile.
Ganuron's will is everything, and nothing else matters.
name: Trauma - Ganuron

description:
You experienced the ultimate humiliation and sense of release that
felt like the end of everything. This memory will flash back in
moments of mundane daily life, tormenting the proud and noble girl
continuously.
name: Trauma - Excretion
